        <p class="lead">HVAC companies that implement email marketing see 15-25% more repeat business and 30% higher customer lifetime value compared to those relying solely on phone calls and door hangers. The key is building automated sequences that keep your company top-of-mind when customers need service.</p>

        <p>Most HVAC contractors leave money on the table by not following up with past customers. A $50,000/year HVAC business can generate an additional $12,500-15,000 annually through strategic email marketing focused on maintenance reminders, seasonal campaigns, and reactivation sequences.</p>
